    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a species of small North American lynx with a spotted reddish-brown coat, long legs, large paws, a rather short body, stubby tail, and tufted ears.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
